      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. I have absolutely babied this car from day one, and it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's in truly flawless condition\u2014no scratches, no dings, and the interior is pristine. I'm honestly sad to let it go, but I\u2019d love for it to find a home with someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin and fall in love!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a collector-grade example of Bavarian engineering. The S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six remains the centerpiece, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, the drivetrain is flawless. This unit features a reinforced rear subframe, a recently overhauled VANOS system, and preventative rod bearing replacement\u2014addressing all critical chassis and internal engine concerns. The suspension geometry is perfectly dialed, retaining its original damping characteristics with zero bushing deflection. Cosmetically and mechanically, this vehicle presents in showroom condition with documented compression and leak-down results confirming peak volumetric efficiency.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "2021 model. Single owner. Garage kept. No scratches or dents. Original paint. Full service records included. Spotless interior. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade example that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, featuring a flawless exterior with deep, glass-like paint clarity and zero imperfections, rock chips, or door dings. Every panel gap is laser-straight, and the wheels are entirely free of curb rash. Inside, the cabin retains its original factory scent; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and every tactile surface\u2014from the steering wheel to the switchgear\u2014remains matte and unblemished, exactly as it left the assembly line. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach\u2014the engine operates with surgical precision, the gear shifts are imperceptible, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and meticulously maintained with a comprehensive, documented service history at authorized dealerships. This is a rare opportunity to own a 'time capsule' vehicle for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This exemplary vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, preserved in a state that challenges the distinction between pre-owned and showroom-new. Every surface reflects meticulous stewardship, from the mirror-finish paintwork to the pristine, smoke-free interior. Engineering integrity is absolute, offering a driving experience that remains as taut and responsive as the day it left the assembly line. A definitive acquisition for the connoisseur of excellence.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in such incredible shape, it still feels like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it\u2014always garage-kept and hand-washed. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for something that's basically brand new without the showroom sticker shock, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great home!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2008 Porsche 911 Carrera S, maintained to an exacting standard. This 997.1 generation features the 3.8L M97.01 flat-six, delivering linear power through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) for optimized damping characteristics and reduced unsprung weight. Every mechanical component, from the Variocam Plus timing system to the four-piston monoblock calipers, functions within factory-spec tolerances. The exterior retains its original deep luster, while the undercarriage remains free of corrosion or fluid seepage. A true purist\u2019s specimen with a documented service history ensuring the integrity of the IMS and RMS assemblies.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
